He ends lectures early and shows up late occasionally. He's very approachable so don't be afraid to ask him for help both in class and during his office hours. I learned a lot!

AWESOOOMME PRROOOFF..HE IS CLEAR AND CONCISE WITH EVERYTHING HE TEACHES. I RECOMMEND HIM FOR ANYONE WHO IS TAKING FIRST YEAR ENGLISH ESSAY WRITING COURSE!
